name: Tessa Fowler
description:
Tessa Fowler, pinup glamour model LoRa.

Use trigger words 'Tessa Fowler', and optionally 'wearing glasses' to add her signature black frames. Try [red hair] or [red lipstick] to accent. Works well 0.7-.85 weight. LoRa is nsfw so add to negative prompt.

See version for training details.

modelVersions.name: v1
modelVersions.description:
First and final version. 53 images of no glasses, 43 images of glasses, ranging from tight chin-forehead crop, shoulders, to full body. Trained in WebUI 2.1.6 using Dreambooth extension on SDv1.5.

Training details:

  • Steps per image: 100 (with several restarts)

  • Batch Size: 3, GA: 3

  • LR Sched: constant

  • Unet LR: 0.00002

  • Text LR: 0.000005

  • Regularization using 'sexywoman' images from HF.

  • Max resolution 1024 using buckets.

  • Concepts using 'photo of <trigger word> woman'

  • Dim, Alpha 64
